      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "THE HISTORY TIGER PARKAmazing Life Expreriences That Will Completely Change Your PerspectiveWe are Tiger Park, a private company where different with another place, the most exciting, attractive. We have experience width the TIGERS for 20 year. We have 4 brachers and over 300 tigers are under our care.Our goal is to ensure that all of tigers will live in the natural environments that make them feel safe, happy comfortable throughout their lives."
          }
        ]
      },
